; Spindle: initial speed, mid-program speed change while running (regression H6),
; and CSS G96 (regression H4). Watch SPINDLE_ON css_factor / mid-run SET speed.
G21 G90 G94
M3 S1000            ; spindle on CW at 1000 rpm
G0 X0 Y0 Z5
G1 Z0 F300
S2000               ; change speed WHILE running (H6: should retune spindle)
G1 X10 F600
G96 D3000 S200      ; constant surface speed 200, cap 3000 (H4: css_factor != 0)
G1 X20
G97 S1500           ; back to rpm mode
M5
M2
